HEADWORD: Rousant
<hw>Rous"ant</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(her.)</fld>
<def>Rising; -- applied to a bird in the attitude of rising; also,
sometmes, to a bird in profile with wings addorsed.</def>⟦br⟧
